Brix/Octociz was still firing when he saw the grenade coming at him. 
He tried to dodge, and it hit him in the shoulder instead of the 
back. Not too bad, but it would kill him if he didn't get help soon. 
He droped onto a branch to rest, when he felt the anger in him boil.

Ocoticz! Bronco is coming! You have to take control!

I can't! He's fighting me! He's.....(Octociz slips into a coma)

Brix could feel the changes. The hatred. The need for destruction. 
The only thing he was able to hang onto was his Maximal loyalty. Brix 
had once again turned into Bronco, his evil personality. He felt the 
rage building up for Chordate. He jumped off the the branch, and 
tackled Chordate down, pointing his poison horns at his head.

"NOW YOU DIE, MAGGOT!!!"

Bronco fired.
